{"_path":"/posts/dorm-crying","_dir":"posts","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"There is no dignified way to cry in a college dorm","description":false,"category":"poetry","start":"2022-11-04T00:00:00.000Z","end":"2022-11-04T00:00:00.000Z","status":"finished","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"there-is-no-dignified-way-to-cry-in-a-college-dorm"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"There is no dignified way to cry in a college dorm"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Tears want to fall, but if they fell"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nthey'd fall onto the couch which"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nyou share with your roommate."},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nAnd you're not that close."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"At home you have more options:"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\non your bed, on the toilet,"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\non the floor of the kitchen"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n(if you're really going through it)."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"But when you live in a college dorm"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nif you need to cry, you'd just"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nhave to pick between crying"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\ninside, or crying outside."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"I once saw a man hunched over,"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n2 feet off of a scanty forest trail, sobbing"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\ninto his cupped hands, face hidden."},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nWhat I'd give to trade spots with him."}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"there-is-no-dignified-way-to-cry-in-a-college-dorm","depth":3,"text":"There is no dignified way to cry in a college dorm"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:posts:dorm-crying.md","_source":"content","_file":"posts/dorm-crying.md","_extension":"md"}